modDescription:
Tired of using commands for players on your server? Need to wipe someone or yourself and need to get them back on their feet? Testing? Use these books to speed things up. Books for both [Experience](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-experience/) and [Skill Points](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-skill-points/) in values from 1 to 500000 will help anyone reclaim what is theirs. The books are set to Dev Only in CM Menu.

**[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/JaxTeller718/A20ModletsJax/tree/main/JaxTeller718-AdminBooks)**
